  "text": "The largest biome shifts projected by JeDi occur at midand high-latitudes, while a smaller proportion of grid cells change in FI at lower latitudes (e.g., the tropics). [CITATION_1] found similar trends in biome shifts under 21st-century climates using the MC1 dynamic global vegetation model. The north-ward biome shift is consistent with observations by [CITATION_2] and [CITATION_3] , who observed similar trends for the past decades.",
